deck: The crew of the USS Voyager get stuck 70 000 light years away.
name: Caretaker

deck: Voyager receive a distress call from themselves!
name: Parrallax

deck: Johnny Storm is put on trial by Ronan the accuser against the Kree Empire.
name: Trial by Fire

deck: Doctor Doom switches his mind with Reed Richards, putting him in the perfect position to destroy the team.
name: Doomed

deck: After believing Reed caused the cosmic storm accident on purpose Ben, Sue and Johnny are captured by Doom's robots while Doom steals Reed Richard's dimensional gauntlet to create a portal to the negative zone.
name: Doomsday

deck: Reed's effort to help his friend Bruce Banner brings the Four into conflict with the Hulk and the people who are trying to capture him.
name: Hard Knocks

deck: Accidental contact with energy from a probe sent to the Microverse causes the quartet to start shrinking.
name: World's Tiniest Heroes

deck: While showing off Reed's lab, Johnny and his latest girlfriend become trapped into the Negative Zone, infesting the Baxter Building with alien bugs in the process.
name: Zoned Out

deck: Namor, the ruler of Atlantis, clashes with the Fantastic Four when he declares the world's oceans to be forbidden to humans.
name: Imperius Rex

deck: Philip Masters, a sculptor frustrated with his lack of recognition, gains the power to control people when a piece of the cosmic ray-bombarded space station falls from the sky and gives his clay the power to control people.
name: Puppet Master

deck: One of Reed's returning space probes is followed by an annoying alien with the ability to turn himself into anything.
name: Impossible

deck: The Mole Man seeks out Ben Grimm as an ally as he pulls famous Manhattan landmarks down into his kingdom of Subterranea.
name: Molehattan

deck: Optimus Prime and the Autobots investigate the return of the Decepticons while being forced to account for a group of young humans who have unwittingly become involved in their centuries-old conflict.
name: Darkness Rising Part 1

deck: An enormous subterranean creature attacks the Baxter Building looking for one of its eggs, which was secretly placed there by the Mole Man.
name: De-Mole-Ition

deck: An energy disruption during Reed's latest attempt to cure Ben causes the quartet to switch powers with each other.
name: Bait & Switch

deck: An energy sphere transports the Fantastic Four to the Negative Zone, where they are used by Doom to distract the insect conqueror Annihilus so that he can steal Annihilus's cosmic control rod.
name: Annihilation

deck: The Autobots try to get Cliffjumper back, unaware of what the Decepticons have done to him.
name: Darkness Rising  Part 2

deck: Ronan the Accuser gives a Skrull the powers of the Fantastic Four, who then uses them to defeat the super-powered team.
name: Revenge of the Skrulls

deck: Optimus and Ratchet head out to investigate Megatron's activities and Arcee and Bumblebee go on patrol, leaving Bulkhead in charge. But things start getting messy when Fowler is abducted.
name: Darkness Rising Part 3

deck: The Puppet Master uses his controlling clay to turn the city against the Fantastic Four.
name: Strings

deck: While Optimus and Ratchet battle Megatron's Terrorcon horde, the others attempt to rescue Agent Fowler.
name: Darkness Rising Part 4

deck: Doctor Doom launches the Baxter Building into space.
name: Doomsday Plus One

deck: The Autobots race to stop Megatron from raising an undead army on Cybertron.
name: Darkness Rising Part 5

deck: Reed succeeds in reversing the Thing's condition, though the now-human Ben Grimm no longer has any memory of the team's transformation into the Fantastic Four.
name: The Cure

deck: A new super-powered quartet upstages the Fantastic Four.
name: Frightful

deck: The Fantastic Four return from a trip to the past to find Doom has changed history and is in control of the world.
name: Out of Time

deck: While Skyquake battles Optimus Prime, Starscream recovers the nearly dead Megatron.
name: Masters and Students

deck: Dethroned by Attuma the Barbarian, Namor turns to the Fantastic Four for help in reclaiming his kingdom.
name: Atlantis Attacks

deck: After several attacks from Iron Man suits, the Fantastic Four track down Tony Stark. It turns out Doom was behind the attacks, and now the Four have to face both Iron Doom and Iron Man under Doom's control.
name: Shell Games

deck: While Optimus and Arcee are trapped in the Arctic, the base is invaded by deadly Scraplets.
name: Scrapheap

description:
Plot Summary

With a big test looming, our favorite idiots receive an education in cheating when Principal McVicker tries to learn 'em good. Will No Child Left Behind give the boys the leg up they need to pass, or are they up No. 2 creek without a pencil?
name: School Test

description:
Plot Summary

Beavis and Butt-Head can't handle the truth! After witnessing a brutal beating that leaves one man out cold, will the boys lie under oath to protect their idol Todd? If they screw up, there's a serious butt-kicking on the docket, Todd-style.
name: Snitchers

deck: Bulkhead awaits the arrival of his friend Wheeljackwhat could go wrong?
name: Con Job

deck: Now that their quest to summon the eternal dragon has come to a rip-roaring conclusion, Goku decides to renew Roshi's offer to come and train with him. The venerable master's first task is for Goku to find him a 'pretty girl.' Will Goku successfully pull off this request, or will he fall short of this vital first hurtle? Who knows!
name: Goku's Rival

deck: After exposure to a potion during a battle with the alchemist Diablo, Johnny finds his powers greatly increased and his personality turning evil.
name: Johnny Storm and the Potion of Fire

deck: The Autobots assist Fowler with transporting a nuclear device.
name: Convoy

deck: Frustrated by his repeated defeats at their hands, Ronan the Accuser asks the powerful Grandmaster to stage a contest that would give him the chance to beat the Fantastic Four.
name: Contest of Champions

deck: While attacking the Fantastic Four, Doom's latest robot develops sentience.
name: Doom's Word Is Law

deck: Terminus, an enormous armored alien, arrives on Earth to plunder it of its resources.
name: Scavenger Hunt

deck: When Bulkhead makes a discovery in Greece, the race is on to recover an Energon Harvester.
name: Deus ex Machina

deck: The duel with Yuma's teacher, MR. Kay continues on. Can Yuma pull out a victory against such a powerful adversary?
name: "Countdown of Reversal! The Countermeasure Is Astral!?"

deck: Yuma is suckered into a duel with his numbers card "Number 39 Utopia" and Astral existence in this world at stake with a boy from his class named nicknamed "Flip" (because he says everything and everyone "flip side to it")
name: The Other Side Where the Other Side of the Duel Is Read

deck: Part 2 of the duel between Yuma and Flip, can Yuma overcome the odds and defeat a foe that has control over 2 Numbers and among those controlled is his trump card; "Number 39 Utopia"
name: " The Treacherous Numbers!?"

deck: Knock Out and Jack are both drawn into the world of street racing.
name: Speed Metal

deck: When Arcee takes Jack on a routine mission, Airachnid turns up, putting him in danger.
name: Predatory

deck: Yuma must win to save Nelson from the Sparrow; the latter alter ego who is possssed by a "Number" card
name: "Lavish Feats of Justice! Calling on Espar Robin!!"

deck: When Optimus is infected by a Decepticon plague, Arcee and Bumblebee sneak aboard the Nemesis to find a cure.
name: Sick Mind

deck: The final conclusion between the duel of Yuma and "The Sparrow" comes to an end.
name: "Star Robin Is Forever"

deck: Megatron attempts to resurrect himself using Dark Energon by controlling Bumblebee's mind.
name: Out of His Head

deck: After a GroundBridge failure, the kids are flung into another dimension with a reanimated Skyquake.
name: Shadowzone

deck: Breakdown is captured by MECH, and the only ones who can save him are... Team Prime.
name: Operation: Breakdown

deck: When Kotori is "kidnapped" by a mysterious foe, Yuma must duel to save his friend.
name: "Cat surprise-Cat Deck!?

description: After the events of "Greetings From Genosha", Nightcrawler is a prisoner of Magneto. However, that all soon changes when he and the Scarlet Witch are teleported by the inter-dimensional show host Mojo to his show, Hunting Grounds. There, they must survive hordes of obstacles and ultimately... Wolverine?!
name: Hunting Grounds

deck: The sisters discover they're witches.
name: Something Wicca This Way Comes

deck: Prue and Piper must saved Phoebe from a demon.
name: I've Got You Under My Skin

deck: The Charmed ones are reunited with their father.
name: Thank You For Not Morphing

deck: Piper falls for a ghost and the Charmed ones must find out what happen to him.
name: Dead Man Dating

deck: Buffy must stop the Anointed One from reaching The Master.
name: Never Kill A Boy On the First Date.

deck: Xander is possessed by a spirit of a demonic bread of hyenas.
description: During a field trip to the Sunndydale Zoo, Xander and four other students enter a quarantined hyena enclosure. Afterwards they begin to exhibit oddly aggressive behavior.
name: The Pack

deck: Buffy learns the truth about Angel. Buffy and Angel share their first kiss.
name: Angel

deck: Airachnid teams up with MECH to get revenge on Arcee and Jack.
name: Crisscross

description:
Hoping to shut down Bolivar Trask and his Sentinels for good, Wolverine leads Forge and Kitty undercover to assault his laboratory. Meanwhile in the future, Professor X and the future mutants are on the run from a horde of sentinels, and the only way to shake them is to head towards a desert known as the Badlands. In this place, lifeless metal comes to life!

Sound familiar?
name: Badlands

deck:
When Yuma's friends realize the revelation that Yuma has only been winning his duels because of Astral and his powerful "Number" monster Number 39: Utopia, Yuma set's off to win a competition with out Astral.
 At the same time, Shark has fallen since his lost to Yuma and has lost credibility as a duelist. Shark starts to miss class and hang out with a gang that is up to nothing but trouble. Yuma then finds out about Shark and challenges him to a duel to save Shark from "himself".
name: "Sharks Counterattack!"
